    "body": "Extract KV cache update op from flashinfer similar to https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/25954\nThis PR is a part of https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/32335\n\n#### Eval (`Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B-FP8`):\nmain:\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8370|±  |0.0102|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8946|±  |0.0085|\n\nthis PR:\n|Tasks|Version|     Filter     |n-shot|  Metric   |   |Value |   |Stderr|\n|-----|------:|----------------|-----:|-----------|---|-----:|---|-----:|\n|gsm8k|      3|flexible-extract|     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8370|±  |0.0102|\n|     |       |strict-match    |     5|exact_match|↑  |0.8946|±  |0.0085|",
